{"tid":1772692,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶] 攰就入黎放鬆下啦","createTime":"2019-12-07T00:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T00:58:29.000Z","uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"345c90f6e77d5684b167e59737bc1f11209f6ecd","tid":1772692,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:55:31.000Z","msg":"從前有隻井底蛙，有一日佢負負碌碌終於係井底到跳咗出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n井底蛙對依個世界感到好奇，乜都覺得好新奇，好新鮮。<br />\n<br />\n井底蛙四圍行，見到條蛇，佢走埋去同條蛇對話。<br />\n<br />\n「你好呀，我係青蛙，請問你係咩嚟架？」<br />\n<br />\n條蛇覺得隻青蛙好撚on9，跟住同佢講：<br />\n<br />\n「你幫我含撚我話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n井底蛙為咗識多啲嘢，唯有招做啦。<br />\n<br />\n完事之後，條蛇就同井底蛙講：<br />\n<br />\n「我係蛇！」<br />\n<br />\n隻蛙覺得好開心，佢終於識多咗個朋友。佢發現原來井外面嘅世界真係好大。<br />\n<br />\n井底蛙繼續探索未知嘅世界。佢沿住河邊行，見到隻河馬，就埋去打招呼：<br />\n<br />\n「你好呀，我係青蛙，請問你係咩嚟架？」<br />\n<br />\n隻河馬見隻青蛙咁on9嘅問題都問得出，於是同隻青蛙講：<br />\n<br />\n「你幫我含撚我話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n井底蛙為咗識多啲嘢，就走埋去幫隻河馬含撚。<br />\n<br />\n隻河馬口爆咗隻青蛙之後，就同佢講：<br />\n<br />\n「我叫河馬！」<br />\n<br />\n井底蛙唔介意幫其他動物含撚，只要識到新事物或者新朋友，就覺得點都值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n井底蛙跳到去草叢，見到隻兔仔，佢好開心，終於見到有啲係同佢差唔多size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢行埋去同兔仔講：<br />\n<br />\n「你好呀，我係青蛙，請問你係咩嚟架？」<br />\n<br />\n隻兔仔覺得佢好撚毒，唔多想理佢，就答青蛙：<br />\n<br />\n「你幫我含撚我話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n井底蛙當然招做，因為佢覺得係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兔仔爽完之後，就話：<br />\n<br />\n「我係白兔！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住井底蛙又繼續佢嘅旅程，重重覆覆，含咗幾多條撚我真係唔記得啦唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n井底蛙跳到去火山附近，佢覺得好熱，熱到覺得唔係好適合自己生活，佢諗住向第二個方向繼續冒險嘅時後，佢見到一隻紅紅地色嘅火加加"},{"pid":"769a39e21f5da5376d53aa6edafdc6a52e115573","tid":1772692,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}